title: Studio in Minneapolis | Stradford Flats
posting_body: ['Studio | 1 Bathroom | $839/month | 374 Sq.', 'Feet', 'Stradford Flats offers studio and one bedroom units in the heart of Minneapolis just blocks from Eat Street restaurants on Nicollet Avenue, the Minneapolis Convention Center, the Minneapolis Sculpture Garden, and Walker Art Center.', 'Catch a game or concert at Target Center or Target Field, and spend your evenings enjoying Minneapolis’ Downtown nightlife.', 'Bike paths, bus routes and the Light Rail make getting around the city simple.', 'Situated in the center of three of Minneapolis’ most exciting neighborhoods; Downtown, Uptown, and Loring Park, these newly renovated apartments provide true neighborhood experience.', 'Stradford Flats apartments feature air conditioning, spacious layouts, new appliances and vinyl plank wood flooring, laundry facilities, bicycle storage and community room.', 'Stradford flats welcomes you home with a friendly management staff and 24-hour maintenance team.', 'Building Amenities', 'Heat/Water/Trash Included', 'Controlled Access Entry', '24-Hour Maintenance', 'On-Site Management', 'Laundry Facilities', 'Smoke-Free', 'Convenient Location', 'Community Room', 'Bicycle Storage', 'Unit Amenities', '7 Floor Plan Options', 'Air Conditioning', 'Central Heat', 'Spacious Layouts', 'Vinyl Plank Wood Flooring', 'Plenty of Cabinet Space', 'Merlot Finished Cabinets', 'New Appliances (Refrigerator, Oven, Microwave)', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
